                <span class="field-content"><a href="/alberta-works-week-open-house"><h2>Alberta Works Week Open House</h2></a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-rightimg-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="/alberta-works-week-open-house" class="imagecache imagecache-thumb imagecache-linked imagecache-thumb_linked"><img src="http://barrheadchamberofcommerce.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/thumb/jobweek.png" alt="Alberta Works Week Open House" title="" width="135" height="170" class="imagecache imagecache-thumb"/></a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>What<br />
Get the information and tools you need on career planning, job search, resumes and community supports.</p>
<p>Where<br />
Barrhead Alberta Works Centre<br />
Provincial Building<br />
6203 – 49 Street</p>
<p>When<br />
Wednesday, April 27, 2016<br />
1:00 p.m. – 3:00 p.m.</p>
</div>
