  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>Join the Barrhead Chamber of Commerce and our guest speaker Joe Ceci (Minister of Finance) on April 21, 2016.  Meetings start at noon in the Multi-Purpose Room next to the Agrena.</p>
