                <span class="field-content"><a href="/earth-hour"><h2>Join Us for Earth Hour</h2></a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-rightimg-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="/earth-hour" class="imagecache imagecache-thumb imagecache-linked imagecache-thumb_linked"><img src="http://barrheadchamberofcommerce.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/thumb/Earth-Hour%5B1%5D_0.jpeg" alt="Earth Hour" title="" width="150" height="84" class="imagecache imagecache-thumb"/></a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p><strong>Saturday, March 19 at 8:30 PM - 9:30 PM is Earth hour. If we reduce the amount of energy we use as a community we are entered to win $7500, $5000, or $2500.  If Barrhead wins the proceeds will go towards the swimming pool so it’s a great cause! </strong></p>
<p>Can everyone please pass on this information!! Help us win funds for the New Pool</p>
</div>
