  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="/student/student-month-october-2015"><h2>Student of the Month October 2015</h2></a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-rightimg-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="/student/student-month-october-2015" class="imagecache imagecache-thumb imagecache-linked imagecache-thumb_linked"><img src="http://barrheadchamberofcommerce.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/thumb/October-Student-of-the-month.png" alt="" title="" width="150" height="119" class="imagecache imagecache-thumb"/></a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>The Chamber of Commerce wants to congratulate Ray Barendregt from Haitel's Garage for our Student of the Month for October. Ray has been working at Haitel's since July and has really shone as a hard working student, someone who is always up to a challenge and willing to learn more. Ray wins a 50$ gift certificate compliments of Grizzly Trail Motors.</p>
</div>
  </div>
  
