                <tr class="row-11 row-last">
                  <td class="col-1 col-first">
              
  <div class="views-field-title">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="/about"><h2>Barrhead &amp; District Chamber of Commerce</h2></a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-rightimg-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><a href="/about" class="imagecache imagecache-thumb imagecache-linked imagecache-thumb_linked"><img src="http://barrheadchamberofcommerce.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/thumb/images_0.jpg" alt="chamber" title="" width="128" height="56" class="imagecache imagecache-thumb"/></a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>The Barrhead &amp; District Chamber of Commerce has been in operation for over 50 years. Our goal is to provide a voice for and a network for businesses in the community.</p>
<p>The Chamber in Barrhead is very active. Meetings host guest speakers that are held the 3rd Thursday of the month at the Arena multi purpose room. No meetings July and August. Partnering with and sponsoring other groups in the community, we hope to make Barrhead the best place to conduct business!</p>
</div>
  </div>
  
